OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS tourists fined for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsneaking into Rome's       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FColosseum for a beer       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, If you've travelled to Rome, you may   
OL,6, have been warned that drinks in popular
OL,7, tourist spots can be rather expensive. 
OL,9,FWell, earlier this week, two American  
OL,10,Ftravellers likely racked up one of the 
OL,11,Fpriciest drinks bills in the Italian   
OL,12,Fcapital's long history.                
OL,14,FThe pair, both in their 20s, snuck into
OL,15,Fthe Colosseum in the early hours of    
OL,16,FMonday morning to enjoy a beer.        
OL,18,FThey were spotted sitting on the second
OL,19,Fring of the ancient gladiator stadium  
OL,20,Fat about 05:30 local time (04:30 GMT). 
